<h2 id="what-is-enclomiphene">What Is Enclomiphene?</h2>

<p>Enclomiphene is a <strong>selective estrogen receptor modulator (SERM)</strong> that stimulates your body to produce more testosterone naturally. Unlike traditional TRT (which replaces testosterone), enclomiphene works by blocking estrogen receptors in your hypothalamus and pituitary gland, triggering increased LH and FSH production.</p>

