  <li><strong>Mood changes</strong> (10-15%) - increased emotionality, anxiety</li>
  <li><strong>Gynecomastia risk</strong> (5-10%) - if estrogen rises too much</li>
  <li><strong>Headaches</strong> (5-10%)</li>
